headline: BofA Cuts Domino’s (DPZ) Target to $545 While Keeping Bullish Rating
summary: Domino’s Pizza, Inc. (NASDAQ:DPZ) is included among the 13 Best March Dividend Stocks to Buy. On February 25, BofA lowered its price recommendation on Domino’s Pizza, Inc. (NASDAQ:DPZ) to $545 from $556. It reiterated a Buy rating on the shares. The analyst said the firm reduced its fiscal year EPS forecast to $19.99 from $20.31, […]
